Uttar Pradesh
Dec 10, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Murder, Rape
Description:
			A 14-year-old girl was found dead near Amethi village here this morning.

On information received by the villagers that they had spotted a naked body of a young girl, police reached the spot and sent it for post-mortem examination, Inspector Kotwali Dharacharya Pandey said.

The girl appears to have been murdered elsewhere and her body thrown here at the Khera turn near the village, he said.


